data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Welcome to your newly updated abode! Revel in modern living w/updated windows, new kitchen cabinets & appliances, & charming knotty pine interior doors. Enjoy the comfort of new flooring, a pellet stove and washer/dryer. Ductless heating/cooling units ready for installation.  With two living areas, there's flexibility for every lifestyle. Outside, a large partially covered patio beckons for gatherings in a spacious yard. This home seamlessly combines comfort & practicality! Possibly assume loan, rate 2.875% Current monthly payment is $1637.
